if (!is_file('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: .idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml') != '8f840afa5995416f6eee329dce0a7df0d9df1927') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of .idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml') !== '8f840afa5995416f6eee329dce0a7df0d9df1927') {
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml') !== '93735c16177f3d01149cf907660e074fa8738aca') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: .idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml') !== '8f840afa5995416f6eee329dce0a7df0d9df1927') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .idea/inspectionProfiles/Project_Default.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('.idea/trunk.iml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: .idea/trunk.iml');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('.idea/trunk.iml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .idea/trunk.iml');
	} else if (sha1_file('.idea/trunk.iml') != 'f70b98c6d2b1b6b05d87b2ac85d1ba28a36d182e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .idea/trunk.iml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea/trunk.iml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of .idea/trunk.iml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('.idea/trunk.iml') !== 'f70b98c6d2b1b6b05d87b2ac85d1ba28a36d182e') {
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/trunk.iml') !== 'c3d3c666e1a211291bd1743b6c2fc13c87aad90f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: .idea/trunk.iml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('.idea/trunk.iml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.idea/trunk.iml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.idea/trunk.iml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/trunk.iml') !== 'f70b98c6d2b1b6b05d87b2ac85d1ba28a36d182e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .idea/trunk.iml');
		}
	}
}

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.idea/workspace.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '8d957029a63509c1a5d495f73b66fa4b1358f813') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .idea/workspace.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '2bcf261165ef2478c323413951c1777654021d40') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '2bcf261165ef2478c323413951c1777654021d40') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '4aa60cc74cf28972cea6ab05f8097259ebf6ea8e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '2bcf261165ef2478c323413951c1777654021d40') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): ajax.php');
		}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/oidplus_v1_compare');
	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('dev/oidplus_v1_compare')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/oidplus_v1_compare');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/oidplus_v1_compare') != '801354a3bbff5aec2a63763888f83709a37b25db') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/oidplus_v1_compare');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/oidplus_v1_compare', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/oidplus_v1_compare');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/oidplus_v1_compare') !== '801354a3bbff5aec2a63763888f83709a37b25db') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/oidplus_v1_compare') !== 'bc723d2eebbfcde26b24ad1622d276ba6f40e51d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/oidplus_v1_compare');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/oidplus_v1_compare');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/oidplus_v1_compare')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/oidplus_v1_compare', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/oidplus_v1_compare') !== '801354a3bbff5aec2a63763888f83709a37b25db') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/oidplus_v1_compare');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/test_database_plugins')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/test_database_plugins');
	writefile_12();
	if (!is_file('dev/test_database_plugins')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/test_database_plugins');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') != '4c716febab8eb578293e77b9edbc3b570cd49332') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/test_database_plugins');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/test_database_plugins', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/test_database_plugins');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== '4c716febab8eb578293e77b9edbc3b570cd49332') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== '07e5d1160a6adf8184c068f0651fbc850f44af9c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/test_database_plugins');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/test_database_plugins');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/test_database_plugins')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/test_database_plugins', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_12();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== '4c716febab8eb578293e77b9edbc3b570cd49332') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/test_database_plugins');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') != '179f61b8bb9d869f3136b08786a1fd6946bf053a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== '179f61b8bb9d869f3136b08786a1fd6946bf053a') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== 'eac61bca25b87d322b0a7d853ca0e5e30d3869b9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== '179f61b8bb9d869f3136b08786a1fd6946bf053a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') != 'f7362a562828bd79d5ac81e0b57205df241a5ec4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== 'f7362a562828bd79d5ac81e0b57205df241a5ec4') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== 'd42acbf0ebf035b9398e030b962336bca54517a0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== 'f7362a562828bd79d5ac81e0b57205df241a5ec4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') != 'bcb8bec062d5603f37c9273150c39001850015b4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') !== 'bcb8bec062d5603f37c9273150c39001850015b4') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') !== 'a49319dc3d701166edd44f5db207a71ad4e6f616') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps') !== 'bcb8bec062d5603f37c9273150c39001850015b4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/show_nontranslated_code.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt') != 'e44b3f2a38376ffe00fec1c3523810a4090c649f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt') !== 'e44b3f2a38376ffe00fec1c3523810a4090c649f') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt') !== 'd6e9c82f6b4fcdcc7e74d6a8e6005a5ee90e570e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt') !== 'e44b3f2a38376ffe00fec1c3523810a4090c649f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/feature_oids.txt');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php') != '7e562a813ec5be06a5485d2c1e7af89d431ce263') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php') !== '7e562a813ec5be06a5485d2c1e7af89d431ce263') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php') !== 'b0e25321c1e81f754075d1a856a4156e697ca282') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php') !== '7e562a813ec5be06a5485d2c1e7af89d431ce263') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreDummy.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	writefile_21();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') != '2d64b2622489c49c679e8664bf0b8a62eb9f49ab') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') !== '2d64b2622489c49c679e8664bf0b8a62eb9f49ab') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') !== '5d737f3b09eea75abbe4fab21aea915af50b2f46') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_21();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php') !== '2d64b2622489c49c679e8664bf0b8a62eb9f49ab') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthContentStoreJWT.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	writefile_24();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') != '10c08402289560ae25e6d407ce5f0ecb405225ca') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '10c08402289560ae25e6d407ce5f0ecb405225ca') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== 'de79a28f0df00e98db6f72545c5759ade74fe3cd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_24();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php') !== '10c08402289560ae25e6d407ce5f0ecb405225ca') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusConfig.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_25();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') != 'cb39faa9e903b6facc37807502fff75a003c1a7f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');

	}

	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php') !== 'cb39faa9e903b6facc37807502fff75a003c1a7f') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusCookieUtils.class.php');

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') != '3262a2f2dfbf638fc68220df6e341bcf763cfe8c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php') !== '3262a2f2dfbf638fc68220df6e341bcf763cfe8c') {

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusDatabaseConnection.class.php', $backup_name)) {

			}

		writefile_26();

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	writefile_27();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') != '94b11ee385bf7cec906a5ea70d14a8f5a257d654') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== '94b11ee385bf7cec906a5ea70d14a8f5a257d654') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== '58cf83bca7e80fe6b7302ac269a0f1fd98ffca43') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_27();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== '94b11ee385bf7cec906a5ea70d14a8f5a257d654') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_28();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != 'be8423edfb1ede7d274305e0c57df6a7afe4ae47') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'be8423edfb1ede7d274305e0c57df6a7afe4ae47') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== '9b02c5f28b7893ebf02ac476d114d484e310c702') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_28();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'be8423edfb1ede7d274305e0c57df6a7afe4ae47') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') != 'f17fcbe4618244b344bb8467d92a9f1404ee7694') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php') !== 'f17fcbe4618244b344bb8467d92a9f1404ee7694') {

			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');

			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_31();

			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusPluginManifest.class.php');

if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	writefile_35();
	if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') != '9a7ee39d5ca4b9ca5beb2c230ee0c55294e824ca') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') !== '9a7ee39d5ca4b9ca5beb2c230ee0c55294e824ca') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') !== '9545fd65bdf23d87b5efad79c1955d4e2bc9d96b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_35();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php') !== '9a7ee39d5ca4b9ca5beb2c230ee0c55294e824ca') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update1001.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
	writefile_40();
	if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') != '920e33802acdef316129bb40cb7bf556d852a8cd') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') !== '920e33802acdef316129bb40cb7bf556d852a8cd') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') !== '946b745722de99ad3179efa91cf81c97aff8750c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_40();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php') !== '920e33802acdef316129bb40cb7bf556d852a8cd') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update203.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_43();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != '67ea3ce0ae3af9855e2588b538b0edb207493756') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '67ea3ce0ae3af9855e2588b538b0edb207493756') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '98ba2c6db31efbe31b5930425bce804a7c140e15') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_43();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '67ea3ce0ae3af9855e2588b538b0edb207493756') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	writefile_44();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') != '8284152307b8cc444a53c401d624d7565a839d88') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '8284152307b8cc444a53c401d624d7565a839d88') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '6fbc53c8f009a632e5609055ca7e63497b98b40a') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_44();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== '8284152307b8cc444a53c401d624d7565a839d88') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.css.php');
	writefile_47();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') != 'cb5131b9ed92f8e269e391f96ca9e8299755c8d9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.css.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.css.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'cb5131b9ed92f8e269e391f96ca9e8299755c8d9') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== '698cfab8649fe6ba70eca3250f01c3ff72820e35') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.css.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.css.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.css.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.css.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_47();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'cb5131b9ed92f8e269e391f96ca9e8299755c8d9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') != '200bf6b63d9e7a2bc95fff26e41f917debf11e5f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.js.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.js.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '200bf6b63d9e7a2bc95fff26e41f917debf11e5f') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '87119e8883b2b315b1d9b4879ba93bcf758d1c7c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_48();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '200bf6b63d9e7a2bc95fff26e41f917debf11e5f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
		}
	}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') != '0c7ee12fa8ed8adb7fdacc27634b3b03e74c4e9a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php', 0644)) {

	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '0c7ee12fa8ed8adb7fdacc27634b3b03e74c4e9a') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '431b1e6f85b8ff77634b6afc6c3d251a98c480b7') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_53();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php') !== '0c7ee12fa8ed8adb7fdacc27634b3b03e74c4e9a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/050_oobe/oobe.php');

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') != '8bbd2cfff1958d4df5553d5bef84ab23c05ec36c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== '8bbd2cfff1958d4df5553d5bef84ab23c05ec36c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== '3633b82ac9034396381b20bbc60e42285e2e4f41') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/doi/OIDplusDoi.class.php') !== '8bbd2cfff1958d4df5553d5bef84ab23c05ec36c') {

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/fourcc/OIDplusFourCC.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_91();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/fourcc/OIDplusFourCC.class.php') !== 'e298d76423f626a874e58b52375ff3cc651e7955') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/fourcc/OIDplusFourCC.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_100();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') != '47ada0af5666c58fde0099a365e32c8fcd362b06') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') !== '47ada0af5666c58fde0099a365e32c8fcd362b06') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') !== 'a3e83cb14c5270dc54258b5bef0673a853cc7062') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php');

				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/objectTypes/php/OIDplusPhp.class.php') !== '47ada0af5666c58fde0099a365e32c8fcd362b06') {

			}
		}
		writefile_110();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/OIDplusPagePublicSearch.class.php') !== 'dd4eb9955723434e2a0188421365b1f6dbc534de') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/300_search/OIDplusPagePublicSearch.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	writefile_112();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') != '4b7f561cc18e0e882f211e39c0a5aa0fb7fef8c8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '4b7f561cc18e0e882f211e39c0a5aa0fb7fef8c8') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '4426d7721a8e004e9687d0a15719149bda691fc4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_112();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '4b7f561cc18e0e882f211e39c0a5aa0fb7fef8c8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
		}
	}
}
